- group of similar types of classes , interface & sub-package
- Package name should be in lowercase
Types
1. Built in Packages
    eg. java.util,java.sql,java.net , java.lang , java.swing ,java.awt
2. User defined Packages

Advantages :
1. To categarised classes and interfaces
2. provides access protection
3.removes naming collision


Note : If you import a package using *(all classes and interfaces),
subpackages will not be imported , only classes and interfaces imported